Retrieve SSL certs matching all provided parameters (AND). Each parameter accept multiple values separated by comma, and in that case it works like an OR, so for a parameter to "match", it needs to match at least 1 of the provided values. Since we use commas to accept multiple values, all commas within values must be escaped with a backslash, i.e: RiskIQ\, Inc.
